//Write a script that deletes all documents with name="Holberton school" in the collection school:

//The database name will be passed as option of mongo command


db.school.deleteMany({ name: "Holberton school" })


//whenever we are asked to delete all the docs with a specifications, we use deleteMany() and specify the specific
//however if we are asked to delete only one, we only use the delete() and specify the specifics
